"438","    <div style=text-align: justify;>This report is intended solely for the information and use of management and the shareholders of Hillman Value Fund, the Board of Trustees of Hillman"
"439","      Capital Management Investment Trust and the Securities and Exchange Commission and is not intended to be and should not be used by anyone other than these specified parties.</div>"
